"We use Firebase Cloud Messaging (by Google) to deliver push notifications. "
"An anonymous device token is generated by Firebase and sent to our server. "
"This token does not personally identify you, is used only to send "
"notifications, and is refreshed automatically by the OS."
msgstr ""
"نستخدم خدمة Firebase Cloud Messaging من Google لإرسال الإشعارات. يُنشئ "
"Firebase رمزاً مجهولاً للجهاز يُرسل لخادمنا. هذا الرمز لا يعرّفك شخصياً ويُستخدم "
"فقط لإرسال الإشعارات."

#: web/templates/web/partials/privacy/section_en.html:11
msgid "c. Contact Messages"
msgstr "ج. رسائل التواصل"

#: web/templates/web/partials/privacy/section_en.html:12
